text: Jakob Šubelj (born 1922, date of death unknown) was a Slovenian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Slovenian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Ljubljana
